  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A highly challenging physics-based arcade game about walking on stilts and overcoming obstacles. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1133590/extras/6418426acf07d8c317260bbd4f069503.poster.avif?t=1729860681\" width=512 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1133590/extras/6418426acf07d8c317260bbd4f069503.webm?t=1729860681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1133590/extras/6418426acf07d8c317260bbd4f069503.mp4?t=1729860681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Increasingly difficult stilt walking challenges spread across <strong>60 LEVELS</strong>! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Show off your unique style with a <strong>CUSTOMIZABLE FELLA!</strong> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete with other players on the <strong>ONLINE LEADERBOARDS!</strong> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete with friends in the <strong>LOCAL HOTSEAT MULTIPLAYER MODE!</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1133590/extras/096cad489d279c1f07a747302361c1f5.poster.avif?t=1729860681\" width=220 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1133590/extras/096cad489d279c1f07a747302361c1f5.webm?t=1729860681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1133590/extras/096cad489d279c1f07a747302361c1f5.mp4?t=1729860681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAMEPAD RECOMMENDED</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1133590/extras/6038be647f4e8a52c634db0d6f61c6f1.poster.avif?t=1729860681\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1133590/extras/6038be647f4e8a52c634db0d6f61c6f1.webm?t=1729860681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1133590/extras/6038be647f4e8a52c634db0d6f61c6f1.mp4?t=1729860681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stilt Fella is designed first and foremost to be played with a gamepad. However, it's also playable with mouse + keyboard.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A highly challenging physics-based arcade game about walking on stilts and overcoming obstacles. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1133590/extras/6418426acf07d8c317260bbd4f069503.poster.avif?t=1729860681\" width=512 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1133590/extras/6418426acf07d8c317260bbd4f069503.webm?t=1729860681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1133590/extras/6418426acf07d8c317260bbd4f069503.mp4?t=1729860681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Increasingly difficult stilt walking challenges spread across <strong>60 LEVELS</strong>! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Show off your unique style with a <strong>CUSTOMIZABLE FELLA!</strong> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete with other players on the <strong>ONLINE LEADERBOARDS!</strong> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete with friends in the <strong>LOCAL HOTSEAT MULTIPLAYER MODE!</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1133590/extras/096cad489d279c1f07a747302361c1f5.poster.avif?t=1729860681\" width=220 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1133590/extras/096cad489d279c1f07a747302361c1f5.webm?t=1729860681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1133590/extras/096cad489d279c1f07a747302361c1f5.mp4?t=1729860681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAMEPAD RECOMMENDED</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1133590/extras/6038be647f4e8a52c634db0d6f61c6f1.poster.avif?t=1729860681\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1133590/extras/6038be647f4e8a52c634db0d6f61c6f1.webm?t=1729860681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1133590/extras/6038be647f4e8a52c634db0d6f61c6f1.mp4?t=1729860681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stilt Fella is designed first and foremost to be played with a gamepad. However, it's also playable with mouse + keyboard.</p>",
